00:18:26.772 --> 00:18:29.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You couldn’t come to the studio today
even if you wanted to

289
00:18:30.067 --> 00:18:32.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
because of what I said, right?

290
00:18:32.820 --> 00:18:35.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I’m sorry, that’s not it!
I was working today!

291
00:18:35.447 --> 00:18:39.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don’t mind,
so please drop by like you’ve been doing.

292
00:18:39.701 --> 00:18:42.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Everyone feels a bit lonely
without your presence, Hachi.

293
00:18:42.121 --> 00:18:44.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Actually, it’s me who gets sad.

294
00:18:46.375 --> 00:18:47.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank you.

295
00:18:48.794 --> 00:18:50.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thank goodness.

296
00:19:01.265 --> 00:19:04.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That’s good enough for me.

297
00:19:10.566 --> 00:19:11.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What should I do?</i>

298
00:19:13.652 --> 00:19:14.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I feel so happy.

299
00:19:17.072 --> 00:19:18.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Be mine forever.

300
00:19:21.577 --> 00:19:25.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I’m many times happier now than</i>
<i>when hearing those words from Takumi</i>

301
00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:28.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>which I can’t be sure are true or not.</i>

302
00:19:31.378 --> 00:19:36.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What good is it to keep
this empty cigarette pack?

303
00:19:39.219 --> 00:19:42.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>If this hadn’t happened</i>
<i>between Takumi and me,</i>

304
00:19:42.347 --> 00:19:45.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I’m sure I would’ve fallen for Nobu.</i>

305
00:19:46.351 --> 00:19:48.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I would’ve loved to be Nobu’s girlfriend.</i>

306
00:19:48.979 --> 00:19:52.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>But if Takumi were to come</i>
<i>and see me again,</i>

307
00:19:52.441 --> 00:19:54.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I’d likely end up sleeping with him again.</i>

308
00:19:54.985 --> 00:19:56.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>I probably won’t resist it.</i>

309
00:19:57.070 --> 00:20:00.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What in the world do I want?</i>

310
00:20:01.450 --> 00:20:05.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>If I always get carried away like this,</i>
<i>I’ll never get my hands on anything.</i>

311
00:20:14.504 --> 00:20:19.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>When I woke up the next morning,</i>
<i>Nana was no longer there.</i>

312
00:20:20.344 --> 00:20:22.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>There was a note on the table.</i>

313
00:20:22.971 --> 00:20:24.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
TO HACHIKO
DON’T FORGET TO LOCK THE DOOR.

314
00:20:29.853 --> 00:20:32.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It’s not something</i>
<i>I should be feeling lonely about.</i>

315
00:20:33.273 --> 00:20:35.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I can see her whenever I want</i>
<i>at the studio.</i>

316
00:20:35.776 --> 00:20:37.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Besides, it’s only for two weeks.</i>

317
00:20:40.405 --> 00:20:44.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>After those two weeks…</i>
<i>she will return here, won’t she?</i>

318
00:20:45.118 --> 00:20:46.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
TO HACHIKO
DON’T FORGET TO LOCK THE DOOR.

319
00:20:46.203 --> 00:20:47.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
LOSE THAT HABIT OF OPENING
THE DOOR TO ANYONE WITHOUT

320
00:20:47.412 --> 00:20:48.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
CONFIRMING WHO IT IS FIRST.
NANA

321
00:20:49.498 --> 00:20:53.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Hey Nana… Even now, not a day passes</i>

322
00:20:54.002 --> 00:20:56.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>without me wishing to see you</i>
<i>on the other side of that table.</i>

323
00:20:58.548 --> 00:21:01.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I would call out your name from my heart,</i>

324
00:21:02.761 --> 00:21:03.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>many times,</i>

325
00:21:05.597 --> 00:21:06.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>as many times as it takes.</i>

